## Troubleshooting

### Skill not triggering

**Solution:** Use explicit keywords like "use {{PLUGIN_NAME}}" or <!-- TODO: provide an example trigger phrase -->.

### Connection errors

**Solution:** Verify KUBECONFIG is set and cluster is accessible:

```bash
export KUBECONFIG=/path/to/kubeconfig
oc whoami
```

### Permission denied

**Solution:** Ensure you have appropriate RBAC permissions:

```bash
oc auth can-i get pods --all-namespaces
```

